 »Fremden« (Waldenfels) in den Blick und präzisiert sie, indem er Jacques Lacans psychoanalytische Überlegungen zu Angst und Begehren aus einer bildungstheoretischen Perspektive diskutiert.  aThis volume enriches education theory with the insight that education always has something to do with fear and desire. The two belong together.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aAdult educationxPsychological aspects. 0aAlienation (Social psychology) 0aDesire. 0aEducationxPhilosophy. 0aEducational psychology. 0aFear. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aBiografieforschung. 4aErziehungswissenschaft. 4aLacan. 4aPsychoanalyse. 4aPsychologie. 4aPädagogik. 7aEDUCATION / Philosophy, Theory & Social Aspects.2bisacsh  aBiographical Research.  aEducation Studies.  aEducation.  aEducational Research.  aLacan.  aPedagogy.  aPsychoanalysis.  aPsychology.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2015z978311070098508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2015z9783110439687oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2015z9783110438741oZDB-23-DSW08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruyterttranscript Complete eBook Package 2014-2016z9783110489842oZDB-23-TGP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839430231zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839430231423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839430231/original  a978-3-11-070098-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2015b2015  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2015  aZDB-23-DSWb2015  aZDB-23-TGPc2014d2016